L

locate(Object, String) - Method in class JSONHandler
public JSONObject locateObj(String criteria, String doc) { JSONParser parser = new JSONParser(); JSONObject match = null; try { JSONArray file = (JSONArray) parser.parse(new FileReader(doc)); for(Object obj : file) { JSONObject aux = (JSONObject) obj; String nome = (String) aux.get("Nome"); if(criteria.equals(nome)) match = aux; } } catch (IOException | ParseException e) {e.printStackTrace();} return match; }
